While is the second loop condiion in python:

while(condition)
{
}
else:
output(statement)

else command can be used in while but in pythin only.

The most important keywords in loops:

Continue,
Break,
pass

Break: Break out of the current closest enclosig loop.
Continue: Goes to the top of the closest enclosing loop.
pass: Does nothing at all. complete;y out of loop 
doent let it to process

